		<li>Merge branch into `dev` branch</li>
		<li>Upload `dev` branch to Staging</li>
		<li>Content Creator updates "Approval Status" to "Approved"</li>
		<li>Pass deck version number to Content Admin for review</li>
	</ol>


	<h2 class="example_subtitle">Once Content Admin approval received:</h2>
	<ol>
		<li>Merge `dev` into `master`</li>
		<li>Upload `master` branch to Production</li>
		<li>Content Creator updates "Approval Status" to "Client Approval"</li>
		<li>Pass deck version number to Content Admin for review</li>
		<li>Content Admin to approve the deck version using HQ</li>
	</ol>

